    Class and Description
    Value
    The class Value defines a placeholder for the values of atomic HIOA models with a history mechanism that memorise a bounded predefined number of the immediately preceding values.
  • Classes in fr.sorbonne_u.devs_simulation.hioa.models.vars used by fr.sorbonne_u.devs_simulation.examples.molene.pcm 
    Class and Description
    StaticVariableDescriptor
    The class StaticVariableDescriptor contains all of the static information related to a HIOA model variable.
    VariableSource
    The class VariableSource describes exported variables of submodels either to define the connections among submodels when creating a coupled model or to define how a coupled model reexports the exported variables of its submodels.

  • Classes in fr.sorbonne_u.devs_simulation.hioa.models.vars used by fr.sorbonne_u.devs_simulation.hioa.models 
    Class and Description
    StaticVariableDescriptor
    The class StaticVariableDescriptor contains all of the static information related to a HIOA model variable.
    Value
    The class Value defines a placeholder for the values of atomic HIOA models with a history mechanism that memorise a bounded predefined number of the immediately preceding values.
    VariableDescriptor
    The class VariableDescriptor extends the class StaticVariableDescriptor with dynamic information about variables: the owner model and the Java field that defines the variable in the owner model.
  • Classes in fr.sorbonne_u.devs_simulation.hioa.models.vars used by fr.sorbonne_u.devs_simulation.hioa.models.vars 
    Class and Description
    StaticVariableDescriptor
    The class StaticVariableDescriptor contains all of the static information related to a HIOA model variable.
    Value
    The class Value defines a placeholder for the values of atomic HIOA models with a history mechanism that memorise a bounded predefined number of the immediately preceding values.
    ValueHistory
    The class ValueHistory implements a history mechanism for model variables to memorise a bounded and predefined number of the most recent values of a variable in a bounded buffer.
    VariableDescriptor
    The class VariableDescriptor extends the class StaticVariableDescriptor with dynamic information about variables: the owner model and the Java field that defines the variable in the owner model.
    VariableVisibility
    The enumeration VariableVisibility defines the different possibilities for the visibility of variables in HIOA models: internal, exported or imported.
